#. ~ Description for ETC Handguns etc
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds new high muzzle velocity, UPS-consuming guns ammo of which can be hand-"
"loaded mostly from disassembled same-caliber conventional bullets, etc. "
"INCLUDES PATCH OPTION in gun folder which is in items folder to disable "
"overriding of core game guns."
msgstr ""
"新增高初速、消耗UPS的槍械，其彈藥大多可從拆卸的同口徑常規子彈中手工裝填等。包含在物品文件夾的槍械文件夾中的補丁選項，用於禁用對核心遊戲槍械的覆蓋。"

