#. ~ Description for scenario 'Challenge-Vault Newcomer' for a male character.
#: .\scenarios.json
msgctxt "scen_desc_male"
msgid ""
"You were very important to an influential corporation with ties to the "
"government, earning you a place in a self-sufficient Vault should the worst "
"happen. You arrived later than most who knew of it. Something seems very, "
"very wrong."
msgstr ""
"你對一家與政府有關聯的有影響力的公司至關重要，這使你在最壞情況發生時能在自給自足的避難所中獲得一席之地。你比大多數知情者到得更晚。有些事情看起來非常、非常不對勁。"

