msgstr[0] "步槍納米反應堆"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'rifle nanoreactor'}
#: .\items\components.json
msgid ""
"A liquid core reactor with milliseconds of operational lifetime that fits "
"inside a large rifle round case, it has enough power for one shot in an "
"electrothermal-chemical weapon."
msgstr "一種液態堆芯反應堆，運行壽命僅數毫秒，可裝入大型步槍彈殼內，為電熱化學武器提供一次射擊的足夠能量。"

#: .\items\components.json
msgid "handmade rifle nanoreactor"
msgid_plural "handmade rifle nanoreactors"
msgstr[0] "手工制步槍納米反應堆"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'handmade rifle nanoreactor'}
#: .\items\components.json
msgid ""
"A liquid core reactor with milliseconds of operational lifetime that fits "
"inside a large rifle round case for UPS-free electrothermal operation. The "
"product of either a genius or insane survivor atomic scientist, but not "
"both; radiation poisoning will likely doom its maker"
msgstr ""
"一種液態堆芯反應堆，運行壽命僅數毫秒，可裝入大型步槍彈殼內，用於無需UPS的電熱操作。這是天才或瘋狂的倖存原子科學家的產物，但絕非兩者兼具；輻射中毒很可能將終結其製造者的生命。"

#: .\items\components.json
msgid "dosed plutonium slurry"
msgid_plural "dosed plutonium slurrys"
msgstr[0] "定量鈈漿"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'dosed plutonium slurry'}
#: .\items\components.json
msgid ""
"A tiny dose of highly radioactive slurry from a nanoreactor, which could be "
"used to craft a self-charged 7.62mm electrothermal-chemical round. Maybe you"
" should give up and get far away from this instead."
msgstr "來自納米反應堆的微量高放射性漿體，可用於製作自充電的7.62mm電熱化學子彈。或許你該放棄並遠離這東西。"

