msgstr[0] "復裝 7.62x51毫米 EC 軌道彈"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'reloaded 7.62x51mm EC orbital'}
#: .\items\ammo\762ec.json
msgid ""
"7.62x51mm electrothermal, electrically charged round with a discarding sabot"
" encasing a 4gr microflechette and integrated handmade radioactive hazard "
"replacing an UPS. Its microflechette accelerates to the point of spontaneous"
" combustion. Dangerous to shooter and targets alike."
msgstr ""
"7.62x51毫米電熱充能彈，採用拋棄式彈託包裹4格令微鏢箭彈頭，並集成手工放射性危險裝置替代UPS。其微鏢箭可加速至自燃狀態，對射手與目標均構成危險。"

#: .\items\ammo\762ec.json
msgid "reloaded 7.62x51mm EC HV"
msgid_plural "reloaded 7.62x51mm EC HVs"
msgstr[0] "復裝 7.62x51毫米 EC 超高速彈"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'reloaded 7.62x51mm EC HV'}
#: .\items\ammo\762ec.json
msgid ""
"7.62x51mm electrothermal, electrically charged round with a 54gr "
"hypervelocity bullet and a handmade radioactive hazard replacing an UPS. "
"Dangerous to shooter and targets alike."
msgstr "7.62x51毫米電熱充能彈，配備54格令超高速彈頭及手工放射性危險裝置替代UPS，對射手與目標均構成危險。"

#: .\items\ammo\762ec.json
