#: .\items\gun\223.json
msgid ""
"OmniCorp bullpup QR555 covert ops platform uses new subsonic 5.56 NATO loads"
" in several roles, \"quietly\". Identical to the ER555 in furniture and most"
" of its parts, the base model is claimed to combine the best qualities of "
"the M16, AN-94 and AS Val. It can fire 2 or 3-round 'pulses'."
msgstr ""
"OmniCorp無託QR555隱秘行動平臺採用新型亞音速5.56 "
"NATO彈藥，可“安靜地”執行多種任務。與ER555在外觀和大部分部件上相同，基礎型號據稱融合了M16、AN-94和AS "
"Val的最佳特性。可發射2或3發點射。"

